偏导数求和

若f(u, v, w)是可微的, 并且u = x - y, v = y - z, w = z - x, 证明:


∂f/∂x + ∂f/∂y + ∂f/∂z = 0


∂f/∂x 	= ∂f/∂u * ∂u/∂x + ∂f/∂v * ∂v/∂x + ∂f/∂w * ∂w/∂x
	= ∂f/∂u - ∂f/∂w

∂f/∂y 	= ∂f/∂u * ∂u/∂y + ∂f/∂v * ∂v/∂y + ∂f/∂w * ∂w/∂y
	= -∂f/∂u + ∂f/∂v

∂f/∂z	= ∂f/∂u * ∂u/∂z + ∂f/∂v * ∂v/∂z + ∂f/∂w * ∂w/∂z
	= -∂f/∂v + ∂f/∂w


明显得证
	
